animeTitle: I Dominate the Revival of Spiritual Energy
otherNames: Wo Zhuzile Lingqi Fusu, I Dominate the Revival of Spiritual Energy, Master of the Resurgence of Spiritual Energy, Wǒ Zhǔzǎile Língqì Fùsū, 我主宰了灵气复苏
